whats up with the bard nerf movement lately?<br>
<br>
quality of this board has gone way down. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uclammorsz1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Clammor SZ1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/02 6:39:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10676.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> I play on SZ, I do want a pair.  but hard.y a 333 damage *bolt* spell is unbalancing in &quot;pvp&quot; where wizards and necro's can one shot nearly anyone with AA skill Burns =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ualliandrevz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>alliandreVZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/02 7:21:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10676.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> "Personally the biggest advantage I see to the boots is on a PVP server. Situationally they could be quite powerful."<br>
